  "texts": [
    "It boasts the highest accuracy in the validation set, at 0.916, with a Matthews correlation coefficient (MCC) of 0.907 and an F1 score of 0.913.",
    "These results are significantly superior to other models, including KNN-morgan2, RF-morgan2, MLP-morgan2, KNN-drfp, MLP-drfp, and Graph Convolutional Network (GCN).",
    "Models like KNN-morgan2 and MLP-morgan2 also exhibit good accuracy and F1 scores, but BEC-Pred still outperforms them.",
    "The RF-morgan2 model has the lowest F1 score of 0.739, indicating the lowest precision and recall among all models.",
    "Overall, our BEC-Pred model surpasses all other models in terms of accuracy, MCC, and F1 scores, making it the best choice for the given task."
